Since the dawn of time, a war has been fought in secret: the inter-species Armageddon between Penguins and Possums. A conflict the monumental could only stay in the shadows for so long. Soon every human on the planet will be forced to

CHOOSE A SIDE.

description:
Centuries after God’s abdication from the Earth, the seven Archangels are trapped in a losing war against Lucifer and his demonic forces. Unable to ascend into heaven, unable to even die, the Arcs were tasked by the Almighty to keep humanity safe from Lucifer until His return. But as time ticks on, as more and more angels are clawed to shreds by the demons, as angels begin to lose faith and join the hellions, the Arcs must face the real question: what if God isn’t coming back to save them?

Unofficial Free Comic Book Day digital sampler.
name: The Arcs

description:
Miles Morales: Ultimate Spider-Man Volume 1

This new series was continued from the ongoing Ultimate Comics Spider-Man Vol. 2 series and the Cataclysm: Ultimate Spider-Man and Hunger mini-series. The series lasted for only 12 issues, after it stopped due to the events of Secret Wars, where the Ultimate Universe and the original "616" Universe where smashed together. Miles Morales will return with a new series set in the Main Marvel Universe, simply named Spider-Man (Vol.2).

Note: This volume is named per indicia, "The" is only included on the cover.

Collected Editions

  • Miles Morales: The Ultimate Spider-Man: Revival (#1-5)
  • Miles Morales: The Ultimate Spider-Man Ultimate Collection Book Three
  • Miles Morales: Ultimate Spider-Man: Revelations (#6-12)
name: Miles Morales: Ultimate Spider-Man
